node.title: Person dies after being hit by car in Auckland
node.description: The victim died at the scene.
node.content: ["A person has died after being struck by a car in Auckland overnight.\n", "Police say emergency services responded to the crash on Rosamund Ave, New Windsor just before 10am.", "The victim died at the scene.", "\"An investigation is underway to establish the circumstances,\" police said in a statement."]
